TEXT.S: aicu ti tasi i lin (inamirikan: Jolin Tsai; ciniukukan: ; 15 a qadaw na 9 a qiljas na 1980 a caviljan na ) mavan a kisansemenay i taiwan, nalemedaw kemasi imaza i taihuku i sinzuang cy (tucu i ). na patagilj aza sengsengan itua senay nimadju kemasi 1999 a caviljan. napaveli anga paselaw 2,500 kuravan a rikudu nimadju i kacauan katjaivililj tua 2000 a cavilj patje tucu. namasan pazangal a kisansemenay itua kinasenayan na ciniukuan masa sinipukeljang azua rikudu nimadju liawliaw pakatua tjadjaljaw a senay katua ziyan italadj tua senay. ka 2021 a caviljan, aza sinan senay nimadju a rikudu pinaka Ugly Beauty (nguanguaq katua sekulung) na malap tua drusa a kazalan a a duqubi, izua tjaljananguaqan a caviljan a senay katua tjalja nanguaqan caviljan a rikudu. kipalikuzan ikiw rikudu 1019 (1999 a caviljan) Don't Stop (2000 a caviljan) Show Your Love (2000 a caviljan) Lucky Number (2001 a caviljan) 72 (2003 a caviljan) (2004 a caviljan) J Game (2005 a caviljan) (2006 a caviljan) J (2007 a caviljan) (2009 a caviljan) Myself (2010 a caviljan) Muse (2012 a caviljan) (2014 a caviljan) Ugly Beauty (2018 a caviljan) kazalan kinaqepuan a semenay J1 (kemasi 2004 a caviljan patje 2006 a caviljan) (kemasi 2006 a caviljan patje 2009 a caviljan) Myself (kemasi 2010 a caviljan patje 2013 a caviljan) Play (kemasi 2015 a caviljan patje 2016 a caviljan) Ugly Beauty (kemasi 2019 a caviljan patje 2021 a caviljan) kuba timadju nalemindjelj aza kuba pinaka kemasi 2009 a caviljan patje tucu. sunatj 19 (2000 a caviljan) (2002 a caviljan) Jolin 24 (2005 a caviljan) Jolin 6 (2005 a caviljan) (2008 a caviljan) (2012 a caviljan)
